data.description: Welcome to 124 Creeks Edge Dr in Beautiful Sneads Ferry! This remarkable property offers a spacious living environment with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. In addition, it features a fully finished 3rd floor bonus area, providing nearly 500 heated square feet of versatile space. Whether you need an extra bedroom, a home office, or a playroom, this home has the flexibility to meet your unique needs.As you step outside, you'll discover an 18-foot above-ground pool complete with a deck, perfect for cooling off during those hot summer days. Additionally, there's a 16x16 workshop in the backyard, ideal for hobbyists and DIY enthusiasts. For those who enjoy the great outdoors, there's a gazebo, a pergola, and a fire pit area with a fully loaded wood bin ready to ignite cozy evenings.This property is equipped with a whole-home generator!! Say goodbye to power outages and enjoy peace of mind year-round. The water softener system further enhances the comfort and quality of your living space.In addition to these fantastic features, there's also a boat dock and kayak launch for community use, providing endless opportunities for water enthusiasts.This home is a true coastal oasis, perfectly situated close to the coast and pristine beaches. It's also just a short distance from military bases, ensuring an easy commute for military personnel. Plus, you're close to shopping and a variety of restaurants, making daily life a breeze.Don't miss this opportunity to make 124 Creeks Edge Dr your new home - where spacious living and coastal charm combine to create a truly exceptional property.  This is more than a house; it's a lifestyle waiting for you. Come and experience it for yourself!
